HARDWARE REBORN (CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED)

URL: https://lebyopc.com/reborn
Used store: https://lebyopc.com/category/pre-owned

Tagline: "Used Hardware, Reborn — Not just used. Every component is professionally inspected, deep-cleaned, stress-tested, and certified."

Three-stage process:
  1. INSPECT — Visual and electronic inspection for defects
  2. RESTORE — Deep cleaned, re-pasted, firmware updated, performance tuned
  3. CERTIFY — Stress tested, benchmarked, documented with results

21-Point LebyOPC Certification checklist:

01. Visual Inspection — Exterior damage, corrosion, wear
02. Deep Cleaning — Professional cleaning of components and connectors
03. Component Identification — Authentic parts, serial numbers, specs verified against manufacturer data
04. PCB Inspection — Bent pins, cracked solder joints, board damage
05. Power Delivery Test — Stable voltage rails and power regulation
06. Thermal Paste Replacement — Fresh premium compound (Arctic MX-4/6 mentioned)
07. Boot and POST Test — Clean POST, BIOS access, system initialization
08. Burn-in Test (2 hours) — Extended load testing for intermittent failures
09. Temperature Monitoring — Safe thermals under load
10. Storage Health Check — SMART analysis, bad sector scan, read/write speed test
11. Memory Stress Test — Full MemTest86 pass
12. GPU Stress Test — FurMark / 3DMark benchmarks
13. I/O Port Verification — USB, audio, display, network ports tested
14. Network and Bluetooth Test — Wireless connectivity and signal strength
15. Audio Subsystem Test — Onboard audio output and microphone input
16. Sensor Calibration — Fan RPM sensors, temperature readings, system monitoring
17. BIOS/Firmware Update — Latest stable firmware for security and compatibility
18. Secure Data Wipe — DOD-standard secure erase of all previous user data on storage
19. Performance Optimization — Optimal BIOS settings, XMP profiles, fan curves
20. Anti-Static Packaging — ESD-safe foam protection for transit
21. Final QC Certification — QC stamp, test results documented, warranty activated

Additional reborn quality steps (from homepage):
  • 24-hour stress test using FurMark, Prime95, and Cinebench loops
  • Ultrasonic cleaning for heatsinks
  • Fan lubrication
  • Thermal optimization with verified safe operating temperatures
  • ESD-safe double-boxed shipping

Pre-owned warranty (from homepage):
  • 7-day testing warranty on certified pre-owned items
  • Remaining brand/manufacturer warranty where applicable
  • LebyoPC handles RMA support for customers on eligible items
